:"Let Israel hope in the Lord: for with the Lord is mercy, and with him is plenteous redemption.","searchKeywords":["let","israel","hope","the","lord","for","with","mercy","and","him","plenteous","redemption"]},{"verseId":"brenton_psalms_129_8","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":24,"bookName":"Psalms","bookAbbrev":"psalms","chapter":129,"verse":8,"text":"And he shall redeem Israel from all his iniquities.","searchKeywords":["and","shall","redeem","israel","from","all","his","iniquities"]}]